OL,3,CEden Camp Modern History Museum
OL,4,Cwelcomes new owners after 40 years
OL,6,FEden Camp Modern History Museum has
OL,7,Fbeen bought by York-based Continuum
OL,8,FAttractions, the owner and operator of
OL,9,Fseveral popular visitor heritage
OL,10,Fattractions across the country.
OL,12,FThe former prisoner of war camp,
OL,13,Flocated just outside Malton, attracts
OL,14,Faround 125,000 guests each year and is
OL,15,Fknown for its immersive storytelling
OL,16,Fto show the reality of life in the
OL,17,FSecond World War.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
