OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1772193823
OL,3,CEden Camp Modern History Museum
OL,4,Cwelcomes new owners after 40 years
OL,6,FContinuum's brands include York's
OL,7,FChocolate Story, The Real Mary King's
OL,8,FClose in Edinburgh, The Loch Ness
OL,9,FCentre, and Oxford Castle & Prison.
OL,10,FContinuum Attractions secured the
OL,11,Ffreehold of the 5.8-acre site and its
OL,12,Fextensive collection of historical
OL,13,Fexhibits.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
