PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1772193823
OL,3,CEden Camp Modern History Museum
OL,4,Cwelcomes new owners after 40 years
OL,6,FAndrew Pawson, CEO of Continuum, said:
OL,7,F"I remember visiting Eden Camp many
OL,8,Fyears ago and being struck by the
OL,9,Fdepth and authenticity of its
OL,10,Fstorytelling. It has always been about
OL,11,Fpeople ` from the veterans who helped
OL,12,Fcreate it, to the schoolchildren who
OL,13,Fcontinue to learn from it ` and we are
OL,14,Fcommitted to protecting that legacy
OL,15,Fwhile also securing its future.
OL,17,F"Our aim is to invest for the long
OL,18,Fterm, support its dedicated team and
OL,19,Fensure that Eden Camp continues to
OL,20,Finspire guests of all ages with its
OL,21,Fpowerful storytelling."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU}D@WO]
