OL,3,CEden Camp Modern History Museum
OL,4,Cwelcomes new owners after 40 years
OL,6,FEden Camp, a former Italian prisoner
OL,7,Fof war camp opened in 1942, tells the
OL,8,Fstory of The People's War and the
OL,9,Fsocial history of life in Britain from
OL,10,F1939 to 1945, with realistic tableaux,
OL,11,Fmoving figures, authentic sounds and
OL,12,Feven smells recreated to transport
OL,13,Fguests back in time.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
