PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1772193823
OL,3,CEden Camp Modern History Museum
OL,4,Cwelcomes new owners after 40 years
OL,6,FThe former war camp was purchased by
OL,7,FStan Johnson in 1985 with the aim of
OL,8,Fmaking it the world's only modern
OL,9,Fhistory museum ` something he achieved
OL,10,Fwhen it opened two years later.
OL,11,FFollowing his passing in 2015, the
OL,12,Fattraction has been operated and
OL,13,Fexpanded by his children, Howard
OL,14,FJohnson and Paula Peace.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
