PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1772193823
OL,3,CEden Camp Modern History Museum
OL,4,Cwelcomes new owners after 40 years
OL,6,FHoward said: "After more than 40 years
OL,7,Fas a family-run museum, we feel
OL,8,Fincredibly proud of what Eden Camp has
OL,9,Fbecome. The stories told within these
OL,10,Fhuts are as relevant today as they
OL,11,Fwere when the museum first opened. We
OL,12,Fknow that under Continuum's
OL,13,Fstewardship, Eden Camp will continue
OL,14,Fto thrive, develop and safeguard its
OL,15,Fheritage for generations to come."
OL,26,@nD@NOUwD@bO]
