FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1772193823
OL,3,CEden Camp Modern History Museum
OL,4,Cwelcomes new owners after 40 years
OL,6,FPaula added: "Eden Camp has always
OL,7,Fbeen about keeping history alive in a
OL,8,Fway that is engaging, meaningful and
OL,9,Faccessible to all. We are delighted
OL,10,Fthat Continuum Attractions will now
OL,11,Ftake Eden Camp forward. Their
OL,12,Fexpertise will ensure the museum
OL,13,Fcontinues to thrive, while keeping the
OL,14,Fspirit of Eden Camp at the heart of
OL,15,Feverything it does."
OL,17,FThe attraction is open between March
OL,18,Fand November each year and is known
OL,19,Ffor being popular with school trips,
OL,20,Fas well as veterans and their families.
OL,26,@nD@NOUwD@TO]
